{"tid":216380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"由應否送女朋友返屋企個post 睇得出香港男人地位低下既原因","createTime":"2017-04-25T06:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T18:50:39.000Z","uid":110080,"like":59,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51d5652aa87d3bbe11d8bb690df631e3e815f58c","tid":216380,"uid":110080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離有個post問應唔應該送女朋友返屋企<br />\n唔計極端柴灣屯門果d <br />\n淨係講中間距離 應唔應該送<br />\n<br />\n結果 正評竟然多過負評 仲要成堆人留言話要送<br />\n最好笑係講咩唔送如果出事點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你條女十幾廿年人自己返左屋企幾多次呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">洗唔洗日日二十四小時保護佢呀</span><br />\n<br />\n咩年代呀衣家 成春日講男女平等<br />\n點解仲要送女返去 家陣香港地係印度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你條女會出事 你自己就唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係成日咩都就d 女 咪比佢地食住 地位咪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話有車果d 都算 你老尾無車果d 山長水遠來回<br />\n時間都無左唔知幾多 真係聽日唔洗返工果d 小學雞先做得出 除非你同我講你見得好少 咁就唔同講法<br />\n但成日見果d 唔該唔好做壞規矩 係唔係都話送<br />\n<br />\n香港男人爭氣d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86c56b38d3cdc734fe6372669aea06c137e5119","tid":216380,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"f41f454d916215dcf9b50a0aa36dd10482239cb5","tid":216380,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"送人返屋企直頭係浪費時間"},{"pid":"16a5387f90eb2e7e375b070f8e9aa6635a34e0b4","tid":216380,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6fcfd8b2b563f6d337aa79bf078a1c2e845bcbb","tid":216380,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"間中就得 次次都送食得屎"},{"pid":"bcc214bb36e59a1b014dd644baebdf101ea37b00","tid":2163